scoringPlays.text: Eli Wolf 5 Yd pass from Jarrett Guarantano (Brent Cimaglia Kick)
Jauan Jennings 6 Yd pass from Jarrett Guarantano (Brent Cimaglia Kick)
Deebo Samuel 3 Yd pass from Jake Bentley (Parker White PAT blocked)
Carlin Fils-aime 14 Yd Run (Brent Cimaglia Kick)
Rico Dowdle 1 Yd Run (Parker White Kick)
Ty'Son Williams 1 Yd Run (Jake Bentley Run for Two-Point Conversion)

videos.description: South Carolina QB Jake Bentley's pass gets batted in the air and is intercepted by Tennessee's Shy Tuttle.
videos.headline: Tennessee collects first interception of the night

videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano connects with a wide-open Eli Wolf for a 5-yard touchdown to the Volunteers on the board.
videos.headline: Guarantano rips a 5-yard TD to Wolf

videos.description: Rico Dowdle takes the handoff and takes it to the outside for a 25-yard gain to give South Carolina a 1st-and-goal at the 6.
videos.headline: Dowdle 25-yard run sets up a Gamecock 1st-and-goal

videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano hits Jauan Jennings on a crossing route to extend the Volunteers lead 14-3.
videos.headline: Guarantano finds Jennings for a 6-yard TD

videos.description: Off a pitch, Carlin Fils-aime rushes in for a 14-yard touchdown to give the Volunteers a 21-9 lead.
videos.headline: Fils-aime runs in a 14-yard TD for Volunteers

videos.description: South Carolina's Rico Dowdle goes over the top for a 1-yard touchdown to cut the Volunteers lead to 21-16.
videos.headline: Dowdle leaps for a 1-yard TD

videos.description: Bryan Edwards make the grab for a 73-yard gain. Later Ty'Son Williams scores a 1-yard touchdown followed by a Jake Bentley 2-point conversion.
videos.headline: Edwards' 73-yard catch sets up a Williams 1-yard TD

videos.description: On 4th-and-10 and 1:01 left in the game, South Carolina's D.J. Wonnum sacks Tennessee QB Jarrett Guarantano to seal a 27-24 win for the Gamecocks.
videos.headline: South Carolina sacks Guarantano to seal win

videos.description: Parker White kicks one through the uprights for a 25-yard field goal to give South Carolina a 27-24 lead in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Gamecocks take lead on 25-yard field goal
